{
 "name": "RPlog_Meeting_on_the_Sly",
 "title": "A Meeting on the Sly",
 "summary": "At the New Republic Embassy on Caspar, Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard quietly receives the cloaked vice-president of the Caspian Union, Cordelia, for an off-the-books meeting. As Delgard leads her guest through the embassy's grand halls to a secure room, the two diplomats spar with veiled courtesy over the relief supplies the Republic has promised but not delivered, and over the Imperial blockade that has waylaid Caspian-funded freighters. Cordelia, weary and frustrated, lets her diplomatic mask slip and snaps at the ambassador before apologizing, while Delgard explains the Republic's quiet strategy of using independent pilots to slip aid past the Empire. The clandestine conversation lays bare the precarious squeeze the Caspians face between the two great powers.",
